        <p>Hogarth is an implementation and transcreation agency, and during my years with them I worked on a number of accounts; Johnson & Johnson, Acer, Nestlé Waters, Nespresso, Dior, Bookings.com and Coca Cola. My experience on these accounts range from TV commercial and digital campaign production to web development using Drupal. Other notable experience is project management and QC as well as being solely responsible for the Nordic Coca-Cola markets when it comes to scope of work, revenue and client expectations.</p>
